,&quot;line-height&quot;:&quot;desktop:46px;&quot;}"><h2 style="font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:15px;">Welcome to EFDA!</h2></div><div class="uvc-heading-spacer line_only" style="topheight:5px;"><span class="uvc-headings-line" style="border-style: solid; border-bottom-width: 5px; border-color: rgb(219, 179, 87); width: 200px; margin: 0px auto;"></span></div></div></div></div></div><div class="wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-12 vc_col-lg-4 vc_col-md-12"><div class="vc_column-inner vc_custom_1490689853022"><div class="wpb_wrapper"><div class="shortcode-single-image-wrap alignnone  vc_custom_1759396120667"><div class="shortcode-single-image"><div class="fancy-media-wrap layzr-bg" style=""><img class="preload-me lazy-load lazyloading" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D&#39;http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg&#39;%20viewBox%3D&#39;0%200%201200%20620&#39;%2F%3E" data-src="https://www.efda.gov.et/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/EFDA-HQ-1-1200x620.jpg" data-srcset="https://www.efda.gov.et/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/EFDA-HQ-1-1200x620.jpg 1200w, https://www.efda.gov.et/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/EFDA-HQ-1-2400x1240.jpg 2400w" width="1200" height="620" data-dt-location="https://www.efda.gov.et/home-2/efda-hq-3/" style="" alt="" data-was-processed="true"></div></div></div><div id="ultimate-heading-69076957f664755c8" class="uvc-heading ult-adjust-bottom-margin ultimate-heading-69076957f664755c8 uvc-8883 accent-border-color" data-hspacer="no_spacer" data-halign="left" style="text-align:left"><div class="uvc-heading-spacer no_spacer" style="top"></div><div class="uvc-main-heading ult-responsive" data-ultimate-target=".uvc-heading.ultimate-heading-69076957f664755c8 h2" data-responsive-json-new="{&quot;font-size&quot;:&quot;desktop:26px;&quot;,&quot;line-height&quot;:&quot;desktop:32px;&quot;}"><h2 style="font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:20px;">About EFDA</h2></div></div><div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element  vc_custom_1685955797209"><div class="wpb_wrapper"><p style="text-align: justify;">The Ethiopian Food and Drug Authority (EFDA) is a federal regulatory body established under Proclamation No. 1263/2021 and its mandate defined under regulation No. 531/2023. EFDA was established to safeguard the public’s health by ensuring the safety and quality of food, the safety, quality, and efficacy of medicines, the safety, quality, and functionality of medical devices, as well as the safety of cosmetics and other health products. It also regulates alcohol and tobacco products to reduce their consumption and protect the public from devastating consequences of death, disability and disease.</p></div></div><style type="text/css" data-type="the7_shortcodes-inline-css">#default-btn-cccf8a654da0ea8021cff39d0d75df9a:not(:hover){background:#133d58!important}.btn-3d #default-btn-cccf8a654da0ea8021cff39d0d75df9a:not(:hover){border-bottom-color:#0d1921}#default-btn-cccf8a654da0ea8021cff39d0d75df9a:hover{background:#b8bd79!important}.btn-3d #default-btn-cccf8a654da0ea8021cff39d0d75df9a:hover{border-bottom-color:#8b8e6b}#default-btn-cccf8a654da0ea8021cff39d0d75df9a>i{font-size:11px}#default-btn-cccf8a654da0ea8021cff39d0d75df9a *{vertical-align:middle}</style><a href="https://www.efda.gov.et/about-efda/" class="default-btn-shortcode dt-btn dt-btn-s btn-inline-left " id="default-btn-cccf8a654da0ea8021cff39d0d75df9a" title="MORE ABOUT EFDA"><span>MORE ABOUT EFDA</span></a></div></div></div><div class="wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-12 vc_col-lg-4 vc_col-md-6"><div class="vc_column-inner vc_custom_1490689857636"><div class="wpb_wrapper"><div class="vc_row wpb_row vc_inner vc_row-fluid"><div class="wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-12 vc_col-lg-12 vc_col-md-12"><div class="vc_column-inner"><div class="wpb_wrapper"><div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element "><div class="wpb_wrapper"><p>I am text block. Click edit button to change this text. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Ut elit tellus, luctus nec ullamcorper mattis, pulvinar dapibus leo.</p></div></div><div class="aio-icon-component  vc_custom_1550833363344  accent-icon-bg style_1"><div id="Info-box-wrap-2865" class="aio-icon-box left-icon" style=""><div class="aio-icon-left"><div class="ult-just-icon-wrapper  "><div class="align-icon" style="text-align:center;"><div class="aio-icon advanced " style="color:#133d58;background:#b8bd79;border-style:;border-color:#333333;border-width:1px;width:34px;height:34px;line-height:34px;border-radius:500px;font-size:16px;display:inline-block;"> <i class="Defaults-bar-chart bar-chart-o"></i></div></div></div></div><div class="aio-ibd-block"><div class="aio-icon-header"><h3 class="aio-icon-title ult-responsive" data-ultimate-target="#Info-box-wrap-2865 .aio-icon-title" data-responsive-json-new="{&quot;font-size&quot;:&quot;desktop:20px;&quot;,&quot;line-height&quot;:&quot;desktop:26px;&quot;}" style="">Organization</h3></div><div class="aio-icon-description ult-responsive" data-ultimate-target="#Info-box-wrap-2865 .aio-icon-description" data-responsive-json-new="{&quot;font-size&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;line-height&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" style=""><p></p><p style="text-align: left;">EFDA is the National Regulatory Body of Ethiopia which is under the Ministry of Health. The Authority is responsible to ensure the quality, safety and/or efficacy of medicines, food, cosmetics and medical devices.</p><p></p></div></div></div></div><div class="aio-icon-component  vc_custom_1685967836032  accent-icon-bg style_1"><div id="Info-box-wrap-8306" class="aio-icon-box left-icon" style=""><div class="aio-icon-left"><div class="ult-just-icon-wrapper  "><div class="align-icon" style="text-align:center;"><div class="aio-icon advanced " style="color:#133d58;border-style:;border-color:#333333;border-width:1px;width:34px;height:34px;line-height:34px;border-radius:500px;font-size:16px;display:inline-block;"> <i class="Defaults-clock-o"></i></div></div></div></div><div class="aio-ibd-block"><div class="aio-icon-header"><h3 class="aio-icon-title ult-responsive" data-ultimate-target="#Info-box-wrap-8306 .aio-icon-title" data-responsive-json-new="{&quot;font-size&quot;:&quot;desktop:20px;&quot;,&quot;line-height&quot;:&quot;desktop:26px;&quot;}" style="">Establishment</h3></div><div class="aio-icon-description ult-responsive" data-ultimate-target="#Info-box-wrap-8306 .aio-icon-description" data-responsive-json-new="{&quot;font-size&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;line-height&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" style=""><p></p><p class="Default" style="line-height: 150%; text-align: justify;">The EFDA was established as an autonomous federal government body having its own legal personality under the <a href="https://www.efda.gov.et/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Definition-of-Powers-and-Duties-of-the-Executive-Organs-Proclamation-No.-1263-2021.pdf" title="Definition of Powers and Duties of the Executive Organs Proclamation No. 1263/2021, Article 66 (1)" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Definition of Powers and Duties of the Executive Organs Proclamation No. 1263/2021, Article 66 (1)</a>. The powers, duties, and organization of the Authority is determined under the <a href="https://www.efda.gov.et/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/%E1%8B%A8%E1%8A%A2%E1%89%B5%E1%8B%AE%E1%8C%B5%E1%8B%AB-%E1%8B%A8%E1%88%9D%E1%8C%8D%E1%89%A5-%E1%8A%A5%E1%8A%93-%E1%8B%A8%E1%88%98%E1%8B%B5%E1%88%90%E1%8A%92%E1%89%B5-%E1%89%A3%E1%88%88%E1%88%B5%E1%88%8D%E1%8C%A3%E1%8A%95-%E1%8A%A0%E1%8B%B0%E1%88%A8%E1%8C%83%E1%8C%80%E1%89%B5-%E1%88%A5%E1%88%8D%E1%8C%A3%E1%8A%95%E1%8A%93-%E1%89%B0%E1%8C%8D%E1%89%A3%E1%88%AD-%E1%88%98%E1%8B%88%E1%88%B0%E1%8A%9B-%E1%8B%A8%E1%88%9A%E1%8A%92%E1%88%B5%E1%89%B5%E1%88%AE%E1%89%BD-%E1%88%9D%E1%8A%AD%E1%88%AD-%E1%89%A4%E1%89%B5-%E1%8B%B0%E1%8A%95%E1%89%A5-%E1%89%81%E1%8C%A5%E1%88%AD-531-2015.pdf" title="Definition of Organization, Powers, and Duties of the Ethiopian Food and Drug Authority Council of Ministers Regulation No. 531/2023" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Definition of Organization, Powers, and Duties of the Ethiopian Food and Drug Authority Council of Ministers Regulation No. 531/2023</a>. As per Article 13 of Regulation No. 531/2023, the budget of the Authority shall be allocated by the government.</p><p></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-12 vc_col-lg-4 vc_col-md-6"><div class="vc_column-inner vc_custom_1490689869709"><div class="wpb_wrapper"><div class="vc_row wpb_row vc_inner vc_row-fluid"><div class="wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-12 vc_col-lg-12 vc_col-md-12"><div class="vc_column-inner"><div class="wpb_wrapper"><div class="aio-icon-component  vc_custom_1686051839284  accent-icon-bg style_1"><div id="Info-box-wrap-9821" class="aio-icon-box left-icon" style=""><div class="aio-icon-left"><div class="ult-just-icon-wrapper  "><div class="align-icon" style="text-align:center;"><div class="aio-icon advanced " style="color:#133d58;border-style:;border-color:#333333;border-width:1px;width:34px;height:34px;line-height:34px;border-radius:500px;font-size:16px;display:inline-block;"> <i class="Defaults-home"></i></div></div></div></div><div class="aio-ibd-block"><div class="aio-icon-header"><h3 class="aio-icon-title ult-responsive" data-ultimate-target="#Info-box-wrap-9821 .aio-icon-title" data-responsive-json-new="{&quot;font-size&quot;:&quot;desktop:20px;&quot;,&quot;line-height&quot;:&quot;desktop:26px;&quot;}" style="">Objectives</h3></div><div class="aio-icon-description ult-responsive" data-ultimate-target="#Info-box-wrap-9821 .aio-icon-description" data-responsive-json-new="{&quot;font-size&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;line-height&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" style=""><p></p><p style="text-align: justify;">The objective of the Authority is to protect the public health by regulating food, medicine and medical devices, blood and blood products, traditional, complementary or alternative medicine, cosmetics, tobacco, quality control service provider, bioequivalence centers and other products and services entrusted to the Authority to regulate.</p><p></p></div></div></div></div><div class="aio-icon-component  vc_custom_1666169892673  accent-icon-bg style_1"><div id="Info-box-wrap-8597" class="aio-icon-box left-icon" style=""><div class="aio-icon-left"><div class="ult-just-icon-wrapper  "><div class="align-icon" style="text-align:center;"><div class="aio-icon advanced " style="color:#133d58;border-style:;border-color:#333333;border-width:1px;width:34px;height:34px;line-height:34px;border-radius:500px;font-size:16px;display:inline-block;"> <i class="Defaults-group users"></i></div></div></div></div><div class="aio-ibd-block"><div class="aio-icon-header"><h3 class="aio-icon-title ult-responsive" data-ultimate-target="#Info-box-wrap-8597 .aio-icon-title" data-responsive-json-new="{&quot;font-size&quot;:&quot;desktop:20px;&quot;,&quot;line-height&quot;:&quot;desktop:26px;&quot;}" style="">Mission</h3></div><div class="aio-icon-description ult-responsive" data-ultimate-target="#Info-box-wrap-8597 .aio-icon-description" data-responsive-json-new="{&quot;font-size&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;line-height&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" style=""><p></p><div class="col-lg-5 features-text"><p>To protect and promote public health by ensuring the safety, effectiveness, quality and proper use of regulated products through licensing, inspection, registration, laboratory testing, post-marketing surveillance, community participation, and provision of up-to-date regulatory information.</p></div><p></p></div></div></div></div><div class="aio-icon-component  vc_custom_1762433316850  accent-icon-bg style_1"><div id="Info-box-wrap-6353" class="aio-icon-box left-icon" style=""><div class="aio-icon-left"><div class="ult-just-icon-wrapper  "><div class="align-icon" style="text-align:center;"><div class="aio-icon advanced " style="color:#133d58;border-style:;border-color:#333333;border-width:1px;width:34px;height:34px;line-height:34px;border-radius:500px;font-size:16px;display:inline-block;"> <i class="Defaults-group users"></i></div></div></div></div><div class="aio-ibd-block"><div class="aio-icon-header"><h3 class="aio-icon-title ult-responsive" data-ultimate-target="#Info-box-wrap-6353 .aio-icon-title" data-responsive-json-new="{&quot;font-size&quot;:&quot;desktop:20px;&quot;,&quot;line-height&quot;:&quot;desktop:26px;&quot;}" style="">Events</h3></div><div class="aio-icon-description ult-responsive" data-ultimate-target="#Info-box-wrap-6353 .aio-icon-description" data-responsive-json-new="{&quot;font-size&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;line-height&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" style=""><p></p><div class="col-lg-5 features-text"><p>The Ethiopian Food and Drug Authority (EFDA) is currently celebrating Medicine Safety Week with great enthusiasm under the powerful theme: “We Can All Help Make Medicines Safer.” <a href="https://www.efda.gov.et/?page_id=12439&amp;preview=true" title="Read More…">Read More…</a></p><p><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-12435 lazyloaded" src="./ee_files/Web-3-300x169.jpg" data-lazy-src="https://www.efda.gov.et/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/Web-3-300x169.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="169" data-lazy-srcset="https://www.efda.gov.et/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/Web-3-300x169.jpg 300w, https://www.efda.gov.et/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/Web-3-768x432.jpg 768w, https://www.efda.gov.et/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/Web-3-1024x576.jpg 1024w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" srcset="https://www.efda.gov.et/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/Web-3-300x169.jpg 300w, https://www.efda.gov.et/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/Web-3-768x432.jpg 768w, https://www.efda.gov.et/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/Web-3-1024x576.jpg 1024w" data-was-processed="true"><noscript><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-12435" src="https://www.efda.gov.et/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/Web-3-300x169.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="169" srcset="https://www.efda.gov.et/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/Web-3-300x169.jpg 300w, https://www.efda.gov.et/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/Web-3-768x432.jpg 768w, https://www.efda.gov.et/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/Web-3-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /></noscript></p></div><p></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="vc_row-full-width vc_clearfix"></div><div class="vc_row wpb_row vc_row-fluid vc_custom_1496301218483"><div class="wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-12"><div class="vc_column-inner vc_custom_1490364540235"><div class="wpb_wrapper"><div id="ultimate-heading-49506957f6647a839" class="uvc-heading ult-adjust-bottom-margin ultimate-heading-49506957f6647a839 uvc-8178 accent-border-color" data-hspacer="line_only" data-halign="center" style="text-align:center"><div class="uvc-main-heading ult-responsive" data-ultimate-target=".uvc-heading.ultimate-heading-49506957f6647a839 h2" data-responsive-json-new="{&quot;font-size&quot;:&quot;desktop:30px;&quot;,&quot;line-height&quot;:&quot;desktop:46px;&quot;}"><h2 style="font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:15px;">Services We Provide</h2></div><div class="uvc-heading-spacer line_only" style="topheight:5px;"><span class="uvc-headings-line" style="border-style: solid; border-bottom-width: 5px; width: 200px; margin: 0px auto;"></span></div></div></div></div></div><div class="wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-12"><div class="vc_column-inner"><div class="wpb_wrapper"><style type="text/css" data-type="the7_shortcodes-inline-css">.carousel-shortcode.carousel-shortcode-id-3064f5b24237fb36a415570880a5e042 .owl-nav a{width:22px;height:80px;border-radius:0}.dt-arrow-border-on.carousel-shortcode.carousel-shortcode-id-3064f5b24237fb36a415570880a5e042 .owl-nav a:not(:hover):before{border-width:0}.dt-arrow-hover-border-on.carousel-shortcode.carousel-shortcode-id-3064f5b24237fb36a415570880a5e042 .owl-nav a:hover:after{border-width:0}.arrows-hover-bg-on.carousel-shortcode.carousel-shortcode-id-3064f5b24237fb36a415570880